   July 28
   Asbury Park (N.J.) Press on the Iran-Iraq cease-fire talks:
   Peace is far from at hand between Iran and Iraq, but the two
countries foreign ministers are meeting ... to work out a
cease-fire to their eight-year war.
   Neither Iraq nor Iran seems ready to accept a draw yet. ...
   The ugliness and absurdity of the war has blurred distinctions
between right and wrong. ...
   Iraq has used chemical weapons against Iran. ... (Ayatollah)
