what you and your advisers felt would help him politically. But,
I'm interested in what your explanation is for his great deficit in
the polls. You have gone out of your way to say that he's been an
active vice president, but apparently the American people don't buy
that, or if they do, they don't like what they see.
   A: Well, you all are aware of the power of the media and the
power of the press. Maybe it has to do something with the fact that
