have been spread among the people by the opposition.
   Q: On the coverage.
   Q: Mr. President.
   FITZWATER: Thank you.
   Q: Mr. President, if that's all there is _ give us a chance.
   FITZWATER: Thank you, Mr. President.
   Q: Do you feel that Michael Dukakis ...
   Q: Come on.
