   Stock prices drifted aimlessly today in a
sluggish summer session.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, down about 8 points in
early trading, was up 2.14 at 2,133.36 by noontime on Wall Street.
   Losers slightly outnumbered gainers in the overall tally of New
York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 600 up, 628 down and 515
unchanged.
