added \ to 31 on the American Stock Exchange. On Tuesday Texaco
said its 78 percent stake in Texaco Canada was for sale.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
gained .28 to 153.82. At the Amex, the market value index was down
.31 at 306.19.
